        <title>J1939 (CAN) Datalink</title>
        <para>The TCM communicates with the electronic engine controller (ECM) and the diagnostic tool, when connected,
            on the J1939 datalink. Communication on the datalink provides information on throttle position, diagnostic
            codes and other vehicle parameters.
